-hour-long%20rescue%20ops%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720317204000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-111548139%2Cimgsize-3735105.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fsurat%2Fgujarat-building-collapse-7-bodies-recovered-after-14-hour-long-rescue-operation%2Farticleshow%2F111547436.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22On%20July%207%2C%20in%20Sachin%2C%20Surat%2C%20a%20six-story%20building%20collapsed.%20SDRF%20and%20NDRF%20teams%20conduct%20rescue%20efforts%20with%20six-to-seven%20survivors%20feared%20trapped.%20Three%20bodies%20retrieved%2C%20one%20injured.%20Police%20Commissioner%20Anupam%20Gehlot%20confirmed%2030%20flats%2C%204-5%20occupied.%20Fire%20brigade%20present%2C%20many%20trapped%20were%20nightshift%20workers%2C%20intensifying%20operations.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20CITY%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Indo-Pak%20Champions%20Trophy%20Dates%20Out.%20Report%20Says%2C%20%26quot%3BGovernment%20Will...%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPakistan%20are%20scheduled%20to%20host%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%202025%20from%20February%2019%20to%20March%209%20next%20year.%20The%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board%20(PCB)%20has%20already%20sent%20out%20an%20official%20draft%20for%20the%20schedule%20of%20the%20tournament%20to%20the%20International%20Cricket%20Council%20(ICC).%20The%20highly-anticipated%20clash%20between%20arch-rivals%20India%20and%20Pakistan%20will%20be%20played%20at%20Lahore's%20Gaddafi%20Stadium%20on%20March%201%2C%20as%20per%20the%20official.%20For%20security%20reasons%2C%20all%20of%20India's%20group%20stage%20games%20will%20be%20played%20in%20Lahore%2C%20the%20PCB%20had%20said%20in%20the%20official%20draft.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20biggest%20question%20still%20remains%20whether%20India%20will%20tour%20Pakistan%20for%20the%20tournament%2C%20considering%20the%20political%20differences%20between%20the%20two%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%2C%20India%20are%20unlikely%20to%20travel%20to%20Pakistan%2C%20but%20the%20final%20call%20on%20the%20team's%20travel%20will%20be%20taken%20by%20the%20central%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20haven't%20discussed%20anything%20about%20Champions%20Trophy%20but%20I%20think%20it's%20unlikely%20that%20will%20travel%20to%20Pakistan%20a%20final%20call%20will%20be%20taken%20by%20the%20government%20on%20travel%20to%20Pakistan%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20source%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthesportstak.com%2Fcricket-news%2Findia-vs-pakistan-champions-trophy-2025-at-neutral-venue-all-eyes-on-icc-meeting-in-sri-lanka-for-big-update%5C%22%3ESports%20Tak%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20Pakistan%20were%20scheduled%20to%20host%20the%20Asia%20Cup%2C%20but%20the%20Indian%20team%20did%20not%20get%20the%20permission%20from%20the%20government.%20It%20was%20later%20decided%20that%20Sri%20Lanka%20will%20host%20India's%20matches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20being%20asked%20if%20a%20hybrid%20model%20can%20be%20adopted%20this%20time%20as%20well%2C%20the%20BCCI%20source%20said%20a%20call%20on%20the%20same%20might%20be%20taken%20during%20ICC's%20next%20board%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20haven't%20discussed%20about%20it.%20The%20government%20will%20decide%20and%20will%20follow.%20It%20is%20an%20ICC%20event%20we%20can't%20decide%20about%20the%20tournament.%20The%20next%20ICC%20meeting%20may%20throw%20some%20light%20in%20regards%20to%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tainted%20political%20relations%20between%20India%20and%20Pakistan%20has%20had%20a%20major%20impact%20on%20the%20cricketing%20ties%20between%20the%20two%20nations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20last%20played%20a%20bilateral%20series%20in%202012-13%20when%20Pakistan%20had%20toured%20India%20to%20play%20multiple%20ODIs%20and%20T20Is.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720317060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F6c7vm0g8_t20-world-cup-2024-india-vs-pakistan-_625x300_09_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Findia-vs-pakistan-champions-trophy-dates-out-report-says-government-will-6046840%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pakistan%20are%20scheduled%20to%20host%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%202025%2C%20but%20the%20biggest%20question%20still%20remains%20whether%20India%20will%20travel%20for%20the%20tournament.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Findia-vs-pakistan-champions-trophy-dates-out-report-says-government-will-6046840%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Findia-vs-pakistan-champions-trophy-dates-out-report-says-government-will-6046840%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Findia-vs-pakistan-champions-trophy-dates-out-report-says-government-will-6046840%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BIt's%20Just%20Arrogance%20Speaking%26quot%3B%3A%20Kohli's%20Admission%20To%20PM%20Modi%20On%20T20%20WC%20Form%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Virat%20Kohli%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F967-virat-kohli-playerprofile%5C%22%3EVirat%20Kohli%3C%2Fa%3E's%20form%20became%20a%20topic%20of%20concern%20for%20the%20team%20during%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%202024%20as%20the%20star%20batter%20only%20managed%2075%20runs%20before%20the%20final.%20However%2C%20Kohli%20delivered%20when%20it%20mattered%20the%20most%2C%20scoring%20a%20match-winning%2076%20in%20the%20final%20against%20South%20Africa%20in%20Barbados.%20During%20a%20chat%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20Kohli%20opened%20up%20that%20he%20had%20zero%20confidence%20heading%20into%20the%20final%2C%20and%20how%20the%20then%20head%20coach%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rahul%20Dravid%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F174-rahul-dravid-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERahul%20Dravid%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20India%20captain%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rohit%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F857-rohit-sharma-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERohit%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E%20motivated%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKohli%20also%20revealed%20that%20he%20even%20told%20Dravid%20that%20he%20hasn't%20been%20able%20to%20perform%20for%20the%20team%20in%20the%20tournament.%20He%20also%20suggested%20that%20arrogance%20ruined%20his%20game%20during%20the%20tournament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhatever%20I%20was%20trying%2C%20it%20wasn't%20coming%20off.%20Whenever%20you%20feel%20like%20'I%20can%20do%20it%2C'%20it's%20just%20the%20arrogance%20speaking.%20Basically%2C%20if%20your%20ego%20comes%20up%2C%20the%20game%20goes%20away%20from%20you.%20Sometimes%2C%20it's%20important%20to%20let%20that%20arrogance%20go%20off.%20There%20was%20no%20margin%20for%20arrogance%20in%20the%20final%2C%20especially%20with%20how%20everything%20panned%20out.%20As%20soon%20as%20I%20started%20giving%20respect%20to%20the%20game%2C%20it%20benefitted%20the%20team.%20It%20was%20a%20big%20lesson%20for%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Kohli.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22zxx%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F9s6atVgAoA%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F9s6atVgAoA%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20gocvideo%20(%40gocvideo)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fgocvideo%2Fstatus%2F1809226827321196844%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%205%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EKohli%20also%20admitted%20that%20he%20was%20happy%20to%20contribute%20to%20the%20team%20in%20the%20all-important%20fixture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20lived%20each%20ball%20at%20the%20end%2C%20we%20can't