ave%20--%20in%20the%20case%20of%20five%20individual%20House%20representatives%20--%20morphed%20into%20direct%20calls%20for%20him%20to%20drop%20out.%20And%20a%20number%20of%20key%20donors%20have%20threatened%20to%20cut%20off%20funding%20if%20Biden%20insists%20on%20staying%20the%20course.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20do%20not%20believe%20that%20the%20President%20can%20effectively%20campaign%20and%20win%20against%20Donald%20Trump%2C%26quot%3B%20Angie%20Craig%2C%20the%20latest%20House%20Democrat%20to%20break%20ranks%2C%20said%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20House%20minority%20leader%2C%20Hakeem%20Jeffries%2C%20has%20scheduled%20a%20virtual%20meeting%20of%20senior%20Democrat%20representatives%20for%20Sunday%20to%20discuss%20the%20best%20way%20forward%2C%20and%20Democrat%20Senator%20Mark%20Warner%20is%20reportedly%20working%20to%20convene%20a%20similar%20forum%20in%20the%20upper%20chamber.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20what%20had%20been%20billed%20as%20a%20make-or-break%20TV%20interview%20on%20Friday%2C%20Biden's%20strategy%20was%20to%20flatly%20deny%20the%20falling%20poll%20numbers%20and%20concerns%20over%20his%20mental%20and%20physical%20fitness%20triggered%20by%20his%20dismal%20performance%20against%20rival%20Donald%20Trump.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20blamed%20a%20severe%20cold%20for%20the%20debate%20debacle%20and%20insisted%20it%20was%20just%20a%20%26quot%3Bbad%20night%26quot%3B%20rather%20than%20evidence%20of%20increasing%20frailty%20and%20cognitive%20decline.%20And%20the%2081-year-old%20was%20adamant%20that%20he%20would%20not%20be%20pressured%20to%20end%20his%20campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20Lord%20Almighty%20came%20down%20and%20said%2C%20'Joe%2C%20get%20out%20of%20the%20race%2C'%20I'd%20get%20out%20of%20the%20race%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20the%20Lord%20Almighty%20is%20not%20coming%20down.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECalls%20for%20less%20divine%20intervention%20do%2C%20however%2C%20appear%20to%20be%20strengthening.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EInternal%20dissent%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden's%20campaign%20team%20is%20pushing%20ahead%20regardless%2C%20with%20two%20events%20planned%20in%20Pennsylvania%20on%20Sunday%20and%20visits%20to%20other%20battleground%20states%20later%20in%20the%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20rally%20in%20Wisconsin%20before%20Friday's%20interview%2C%20Biden%20had%20delivered%20a%20forceful%2C%20energetic%20stump%20speech%2C%20unequivocally%20declaring%2C%20%26quot%3BI'm%20staying%20in%20the%20race.%20I'll%20beat%20Donald%20Trump.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20came%20the%20sit-down%20with%20the%20ABC%20network%20that%20appeared%20unlikely%20to%20soothe%20the%20concerns%20of%20critics%20who%20say%20that%20--%20away%20from%20a%20teleprompter%20--%20Biden%20can%20struggle%20to%20communicate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20his%20answers%20were%20tentative%2C%20meandering%20and%20difficult%20to%20follow%2C%20even%20as%20he%20sought%20to%20deflect%20questions%20about%20his%20mental%20acuity%20and%20dismissed%20the%20notion%20that%20his%20party%20would%20consider%20replacing%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Biden%20campaign%20had%20another%20small%20fire%20to%20put%20out%20Saturday%20after%20it%20emerged%20that%20the%20White%20House%20had%20provided%20the%20questions%20for%20interviews%20the%20president%20gave%20to%20two%20Black%20radio%20stations%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EOut%20of%20touch%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDemocratic%20strategist%20David%20Axelrod%20suggested%20in%20a%20CNN%20op-ed%20that%20Biden%20is%20engaged%20in%20%26quot%3BDenial.%20Delusion.%20Defiance.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20stakes%20are%20as%20great%20as%20Biden%20describes.%20And%20if%20he%20believes%20it%2C%20as%20I%20think%20he%20does%2C%20he%20will%20eventually%20do%20what%20duty%20and%20love%20of%20country%20requires%2C%20and%20step%20aside%2C%26quot%3B%20Axelrod%20wrote%20in%20the%20piece%20published%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20he%20does%20not%2C%20it%20will%20be%20Biden's%20age%2C%20and%20not%20Trump's%20moral%20and%20ethical%20void%2C%20that%20will%20dominate%20the%20rest%20of%20this%20most%20important%20campaign%20and%20sully%20the%20president's%20historic%20legacy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20sarcastically%20suggested%20Biden%20should%20%26quot%3Bignore%20his%20many%20critics%20and%20move%20forward%2C%20with%20alacrity%20and%20strength.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20should%20be%20sharp%2C%20precise%20and%20energetic%2C%20just%20like%20he%20was%20in%20The%20Debate%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Republican%20challenger%20said%20in%20a%20social%20media%20post%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20now%2C%20Democrats%20are%20largely%20keeping%20a%20lid%20on%20any%20simmering%20discontent%20with%20their%20leader%20--%20at%20least%20in%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20with%20election%20day%20just%20four%20months%20away%2C%20any%20move%20to%20replace%20Biden%20as%20nominee%20would%20need%20to%20be%20made%20sooner%20rather%20than%20later%2C%20and%20the%20meetings%20of%20top%20Congressional%20Democrats%20in%20coming%20days%20will%20be%20scrutinized%20for%20any%20signs%20of%20more%20open%20rebellion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20for%20Biden%20and%20his%20campaign%20team%2C%20the%20strategy%20seems%20to%20be%20to%20ride%20it%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20next%20major%20test%20will%20be%20a%20press%20conference%20scheduled%20for%20Thursday%20during%20the%20NATO%20leaders'%20summit%20in%20Washington.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20pressed%20in%20the%20ABC%20interview%20on%20why%20he%20doesn't%20take%20an%20independent%20neurological%20exam%2C%20Biden%20argued%20that%20the%20role%20of%20US%20president%20meant%20being%20subjected%20to%20constant%20mental%20assessment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20a%20cognitive%20test%20every%20single%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BNot%20only%20am%20I%20campaigning%2