0with%20his%20parents%20when%20he%20was%20four%20years%20old.%20His%20father%20was%20a%20marketing%20manager%20for%20Indian%20Petrochemicals%20Corporation%20Limited%20and%20moved%20to%20the%20UK%20after%20taking%20charge%20of%20a%20British%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Mishra%20grew%20up%20in%20the%20UK%20with%20his%20brother%20and%20a%20sister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20entered%20politics%20after%20completing%20his%20studies%20in%20London%20and%20was%20elected%20to%20the%20House%20of%20Commons%20in%20the%202019%20elections%20on%20a%20Labour%20Party%20ticket%20from%20Stockport.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EIt's%20an%20honour%20to%20be%20officially%20nominated%20as%20the%20Labour%20candidate%20for%20Stockport%20constituency.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnSince%202019%2C%20I%20have%20always%20put%20the%20priorities%20of%20local%20residents%20first.%20If%20re-elected%2C%20I%20will%20continue%20to%20work%20hard%20for%20Brinnington%2C%20Edgeley%2C%20Davenport%2C%20the%20Heatons%20and%20Reddish.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FCtv1CHn58F%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FCtv1CHn58F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Navendu%20Mishra%20(%40NavPMishra)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FNavPMishra%2Fstatus%2F1798363908820079061%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJune%205%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Pandey%20said%20Mr%20Mishra%20entered%20politics%20through%20the%20trade%20union%20movement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Mishra%20is%20very%20close%20to%20him%2C%20Mr%20Pandey%20said%20and%20added%20that%20his%20nephew%20called%20him%20after%20winning%20the%20election%20to%20seek%20his%20blessings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Pandey%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BHe%20(Mishra)%20likes%20coming%20to%20India.%20He%20is%20always%20keen%20on%20doing%20something%20for%20his%20country.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BHe%20visits%20India%20once%20every%20year%20or%20two%20and%20makes%20it%20a%20point%20to%20visit%20relatives%20from%20Gorakhpur%20to%20Delhi.%20He%20is%20a%20vegetarian%20and%20loves%20home-cooked%20food%20common%20in%20eastern%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPraising%20his%20nephew%2C%20Pandey%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20can%20guess%20his%20popularity%20by%20his%20victory%20margin.%20In%20the%20UK%2C%20where%20elections%20are%20won%20by%20margins%20of%20only%201%2C000-2%2C000%20votes%2C%20Mishra%20won%20by%20about%2016%2C000%20votes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Mishra%20secured%2021%2C787%20of%20the%20votes%20cast.%20His%20closest%20contender%2C%20Reform%20UK%20candidate%20Lynn%20Schofield%2C%20got%206%2C517%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Pandey%20said%20Mr%20Mishra%20returned%20to%20India%20for%20the%20first%20time%20after%20about%20seven%20years%20in%20the%20UK%20and%20spent%20time%20at%20the%20home%20of%20his%20maternal%20grandparents%20in%20Gorakhpur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMishra%20used%20to%20fly%20kites%20and%20play%20cricket%20in%20the%20streets%20with%20the%20children%20of%20locals%2C%20including%20my%20two%20sons%20and%20daughter.%20My%20children%20are%20also%20ecstatic%20over%20his%20victory%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20a%20recent%20visit%20to%20India%2C%20Mr%20Mishra%20led%20a%20delegation%20to%20meet%20Gujarat%20Chief%20Minister%20Bhupendra%20Patel.%20The%20delegation%20also%20met%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20this%2C%20he%20spent%20time%20with%20his%20family%20in%20Delhi%20and%20Lucknow%2C%20Mr%20Pandey%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolitical%20experts%20claimed%20that%20Mr%20Mishra's%20victory%20and%20his%20connection%20with%20India%20would%20strengthen%20bilateral%20relations%20and%20cultural%2C%20political%20and%20social%20ties%20between%20the%20two%20nations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Pandey%20said%20Mr%20Mishra%20had%20also%20planned%20to%20visit%20the%20Ram%20templ