tps%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ftv%2Fnews%2Fbiden-abc-stephanopoulos-interview-ratings-1236061718%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ftv%2Fnews%2Fbiden-abc-stephanopoulos-interview-ratings-1236061718%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ftv%2Fnews%2Fbiden-abc-stephanopoulos-interview-ratings-1236061718%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Loyal%20Voters%20Went%20On%20Holiday%3A%20Eknath%20Shinde%20On%20NDA's%20Poor%20Maharashtra%20Show%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMaharashtra%20Chief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde%20on%20Saturday%20attributed%20the%20setback%20suffered%20by%20the%20NDA%20in%20recent%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20in%20the%20state%20to%20loyal%20voters%20going%20on%20holiday%20during%20voting%2C%20under%20the%20assumption%20that%20the%20alliance%20was%20set%20to%20win%20more%20than%20400%20constituencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20acknowledged%20that%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20was%20caught%20off%20guard%20by%20the%20Opposition%2C%20which%20succeeded%20in%20voter%20consolidation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20a%20joint%20rally%20of%20Mahayuti%20partners%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20BJP%20leader%20and%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20supported%20Mr%20Shinde's%20claims%2C%20stating%20that%20the%20NDA%20leaders%20did%20not%20pay%20enough%20attention%20to%20the%20lies%20spread%20by%20the%20Opposition%20during%20the%20campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rally%20was%20attended%20by%20leaders%20of%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20BJP%2C%20NCP%20headed%20by%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Ajit%20Pawar%2C%20and%20other%20small%20constituents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Maharashtra%2C%20which%20sends%2048%20members%20to%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20the%20BJP-led%20NDA%20could%20win%20only%2017%20seats%2C%20while%20the%20MVA%20comprising%20the%20Congress%2C%20NCP%20(Sharadchandra%20Pawar)%20and%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20bagged%2030%20constituencies.%20The%20Independent%20candidate%20who%20won%20the%20Sangli%20constituency%20is%20a%20Congress%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20caught%20off%20guard%20by%20the%20opposition%20during%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Shinde%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20of%20our%20voters%20went%20on%20holiday%20during%20the%20polling%2C%20assuming%20that%20the%20NDA%20would%20easily%20win%20more%20than%20400%20seats%20in%20the%20general%20elections.%20This%20loss%20underscores%20the%20need%20for%20a%20more%20strategic%20approach%20in%20the%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shinde%20claimed%20the%20opposition%20voters%20diligently%20exercised%20their%20franchise%2C%20with%20almost%2080%20per%20cent%20turnout.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%2060%20per%20cent%20of%20our%20voters%20had%20turned%20up%20at%20the%20polling%20booths%2C%20we%20could%20have%20easily%20won%2040%20seats.%20We%20can't%20afford%20to%20be%20naive%20or%20callous%20after%20being%20hit%20hard%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20critical%20remark%20against%20Congress%2C%20Mr%20Shinde%20highlighted%20its%20history%20of%20scams%2C%20such%20as%20Bofors%2C%20fodder%2C%20and%20coal%2C%20while%20questioning%20if%20there%20had%20been%20any%20corruption%20allegations%20against%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Fadnavis%20emphasised%20the%20significant%20impact%20of%20lies%20spread%20by%20the%20opposition%20during%20the%20campaign%20on%20the%20voters%20and%20the%20urgent%20need%20for%20an%20effective%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20MVA%20won%20two%20lakh%20votes%20more%20than%20the%20NDA%20candidates%2C%20but%20they%20won%20nearly%2030%20seats.%20They%20used%20to%20lie%20every%20day%20before%20the%20media%2C%20and%20we%20thought%20it%20would%20not%20affect%20our%20voters.%20But%20in%20reality%2C%20it%20did%20affect%20our%20voters%2C%20and%20we%20could%20not%20counter%20it%20effective