g.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-111542591%2Cimgsize-49048.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fradhika-merchant-grooves-with-nita-ambani-isha-ambani-and-shloka-ambani-on-parineeti-chopras-drama-queen-at-the-sangeet-ceremony%2Farticleshow%2F111542592.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F111542592.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EAnant%20Ambani%20and%20Radhika%20Merchant's%20sangeet%20at%20Nita%20Mukesh%20Ambani%20Cultural%20Centre%20in%20Mumbai%20was%20a%20star-studded%20affair.%20Celebrities%20like%20Salman%20Khan%2C%20Alia%20Bhatt%2C%20and%20Justin%20Bieber%20attended.%20Nita%20and%20Mukesh%20Ambani%20praised%20Indian%20cricketers%20for%20their%20recent%20victory%2C%20with%20special%20mentions%20for%20Hardik%20Pandya's%20resilience%20and%20past%20World%20Cup%20wins.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fradhika-merchant-grooves-with-nita-ambani-isha-ambani-and-shloka-ambani-on-parineeti-chopras-drama-queen-at-the-sangeet-ceremony%2Farticleshow%2F111542592.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22No%20Veggies%2C%20Not%20Even%20Dal%2C%20This%20School's%20Mid-Day%20Meal%20Is%20Rice%20And%20Turmeric%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ERefusing%20to%20be%20outdone%20by%20reports%20of%20children%20being%20served%20chapatis%20and%20salt%20in%20their%20mid-day%20meals%20in%20other%20states%2C%20a%20school%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20has%20been%20giving%20its%20students%20plain%20rice%20with%20only%20some%20turmeric%20added%20to%20it.%20Vegetables%20are%20missing%2C%20as%20are%20pulses%20on%20several%20occasions%2C%20which%20would%20have%20enabled%20the%20young%20children%20to%20at%20least%20have%20some%20khichdi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state's%20education%20department%20has%20a%20prescribed%20menu%20for%20mid-day%20meals%2C%20promising%20a%20variety%20of%20nutritious%20food.%20The%20reality%20at%20the%20school%20and%20some%20other%20institutions%20reveals%2C%20however%2C%20that%20the%20menu%20remains%20only%20on%20paper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20malnutrition%20rate%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20stood%20at%2017.76%25%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bijakura%20Primary%20School%20in%20Bijakura%20village%2C%20Patel%20Para%2C%20Balrampur%2C%20serves%20mid-day%20meals%20to%2043%20students%20and%20officials%20admitted%20that%20they%20have%20not%20been%20serving%20any%20vegetables%20for%20nearly%20a%20week.%20The%20meals%20have%20consisted%20of%20rice%20and%20dal%2C%20or%20just%20turmeric%20rice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20in-charge%20head%20teacher%20at%20the%20school%20attributed%20the%20lack%20of%20vegetables%20to%20non-delivery%20by%20the%20mid-day%20meal%20suppliers%2C%20who%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20claim%20that%20supplies%20have%20stopped%20because%20they%20have%20not%20been%20paid%20their%20dues.%20Amid%2C%20the%20blame%20game%2C%20it's%20the%20children%20who%20are%20being%20deprived%20of%20the%20balanced%20diet%20mandated%20by%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVegetables%20have%20not%20been%20provided%20by%20the%20suppliers%2C%20which%20is%20why%20we%20can't%20serve%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20head%20teacher%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20District%20Education%20Officer%2C%20Devendra%20Nath%20Mishra%2C%20assured%20immediate%20investigation%20and%20action.%20%26quot%3BThis%20matter%20has%20come%20to%20my%20notice%20through%20you.%20I%20will%20investigate%20it%20today%20itself%20and%20action%20will%20be%20taken%20as%20per%20the%20rules%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Mishra%20told%20NDTV%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELocal%20officials%20and%20staff%20members%20of%20the%20school%20also%20said%20the%20lack%20of%20supplies%20is%20to%20blame.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERamprasad%20Ram%2C%20the%20Ward%20Panch%2C%20explained%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20group%20responsible%20for%20providing%20vegetables%20is%20negligent%2C%20which%20is%20why%20we%20are%20unable%20to%20serve%20proper%20food%20to%20children.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECook%20Sukhiya%20Devi%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20we%20don't%20receive%20vegetables%2C%20we%20can't%20serve%20them%20to%20children.%20Sometimes%20we%20have%20dal%20rice%2C%20sometimes%20only%20rice.%20When%20we%20ask%20for%20vegetables%2C%20the%20suppliers%20say%20they%20aren't%20available.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAnganwadis%20Hit%20Too%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20issue%20at%20Bijakura%20Primary%20School%20is%20part%20of%20a%20broader%20problem%20in%20Chhattisgarh's%20nutritional%20programs.%20The%20state%20government%20distributes%20ready-to-eat%20nutritious%20food%20to%20combat%20malnutrition%20among%20children%20and%20pregnant%20women%2C%20but%20supply%20chain%20disruptions%20have%20halted%20deliveries%20to%20a%20whopping%2052%2C474%20anganwadi%20centres%20in%20the%20state%20for%20over%20a%20week.%20Apart%20from%20their%20other%20roles%2C%20these%20centres%20provide%20supplementary%20nutrition%20to%20children%20and%20pregnant%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20inspection%20by%20NDTV%20confirmed%20that%20the%20supply%20of%20nutritious%20food%20for%20July%2C%20expected%20to%20arrive%20in%20June%2C%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20delivered%20in%20many%20anganwadi%20centres%2C%20including%20in%20the%20capital%2C%20Raipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPremlata%2C%20an%20assistant%20at%20the%20Vinoba%20Bhavenagar%20Anganwadi%20Centre%20in%20Raipur%20confirmed%20the%20delay%2C%20stating%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20not%20received%20the%20nutrition%20food%20for%20July%20yet%2C%20and%20this%20is%20causing%20concern%20among%20parents%20and%20guardians.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilar%20reports%20came%20from%20the%20Utkal%20Basti%20Anganwadi%20in%20the%20city%20as%20well%2C%20but%20the%20issue%20extends%20beyond%20Raipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnganwadi%20Centres%20in%20other%20regions%2C%20including%20Pendra%20in%20the%20Gaurela-Pendra-Marwahi%20district%2C%20are%20also%20experiencing%20supply%20disruptions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESangeeta%20Sonwani%2C%20Anganwadi%20Sahayika%2C%20said%20%26quot%3BThe%20delay%20in%20the%20supply%20of%20nutritious%20food%20is%20troubling.%20We%20rely%20on%20these%20supplies%20to%20ensure%20the%20health%20of%20the%20children%20and%20pregnant%20women%20we%20serve.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUma%20Sonwani%2C%20from%20the%20Bhatapara%20Anganwadi%20Center%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20situation%20is%20dire.%20We%20need%20the%20government%20to%20address%20this%20issue%20immediately%20to%20prevent%20malnutrition%20among%20our%20beneficiaries.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'No%20Files%20Stuck'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Chhattisgarh%20chief%20minister%20Bhupesh%20Baghel%20criticised%20the%20current%20administration%20for%20altering%20a%20system%20that%20was%20functioning%20efficiently.%20%26quot%3BOur%20government%20had%20established%20a%20robust%20system%2C%20but%20it%20was%20changed.%20When%20will%20the%20nutrition%20food%20be%20made%20available%20again%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWomen%20and%20Child%20Development%20Minister%20Lakshmi%20Rajwade%2C%20however%2C%20maintains%20that%20the%20distribution%20of%20nutritious%20food%20is%20ongoing.%20%26quot%3BReady-to-eat%20food%20is%20being%20provided%20continuously%2C%20no%20files%20are%20stuck.%20The%20Congress%20government%20had%20given%20contracts%20to%20make%20ready-to-eat%20food%20to%20the%20seed%20corporation.%20We%20have%20assigned%20the%20task%20to%20self-help%20groups%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720285500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fjoh4fpsg_chhattisgarh-turmeric-rice-midday-meal_625x300_06_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvideo-in-chhattisgarh