%20to%20solve%20the%20root%20causes%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMaking%20shawls%2C%20quilts%2C%20and%20paper%20from%20chicken%20waste%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20order%20to%20do%20his%20bit%2C%20Radhesh%20launched%20his%20company%20in%202019.%20Explaining%20its%20functioning%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CFirstly%2C%20we%20collect%20waste%20from%20slaughterhouses%20and%20then%20we%20sterilise%20and%20sanitise%20it%20in%20a%20hygienic%20way%20using%20100%20degrees%20steam%20process%20to%20kill%20the%20various%20worms%20present%20in%20the%20waste.%20Using%20our%20patented%20technology%2C%20we%20use%20natural%20ingredients%20to%20process%20the%20waste%20into%20wool-like%20fibre%20which%20is%20similar%20to%20pashmina%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CChicken%20is%20a%20fowl%20and%20it%20has%20feathers%20similar%20to%20other%20birds.%20Feathers%20themselves%20are%20lightweight%20and%20using%20that%2C%20we%20are%20able%20to%20make%20natural%20wool-like%20fibre%20similar%20to%20cotton%2C%20jute%2C%20wool%2C%20and%20silk.%20This%20woollen%20fibre%20is%20soft%2C%20warm%20and%20durable%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20this%20purpose%2C%20Radhesh%20says%20he%20has%20trained%201%2C200%20tribal%20women%20of%20Rajasthan%20who%20weave%20and%20spin%20the%20waste%20into%20fibre.%20Feathers%20which%20are%20not%20good%20for%20spinning%20are%20used%20to%20make%20handmade%20paper%20or%20converted%20into%20fillers%20for%20quilts%2C%20jackets%2C%20and%20pillows.%20In%20this%20process%2C%20the%20byproduct%20of%20chicken%20butchery%20waste%20is%20converted%20into%20compost%20and%20fish%20feed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fgolden-feathers-1718797164.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22After%2