0with%20their%20parents%20who%20work%20there.%20While%20they%20may%20belong%20to%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20country%2C%20what%20unfortunately%20remains%20common%20is%20the%20fact%20that%20these%20children%20don%E2%80%99t%20go%20to%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20might%20be%20due%20to%20a%20multitude%20of%20factors%20ranging%20from%20frequent%20movement%20of%20the%20parents%20to%20not%20having%20a%20basic%20understanding%20or%20not%20having%20the%20appropriate%20ID%20cards.%20However%2C%20these%20reasons%20pale%20in%20comparison%20to%20what%20these%20children%20are%20losing%20out%20on%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0%20the%20right%20to%20basic%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20it%20happens%2C%20those%20working%20in%20the%20construction%20and%20real%20estate%20industries%20are%20most%20exposed%20to%20this%20social%20problem.%20A%20senior%20employee%20at%20My%20Home%20Constructions%2C%20a%20real%20estate%20company%20in%20Hyderabad%2C%20was%20disturbed%20when%20he%20saw%20these%20children%20not%20going%20to%20school.%20They%20were%20often%20left%20behind%20unattended%2C%20which%20could%20be%20extremely%20dangerous.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201512px)%20100vw%2C%201512px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fmeru-daycare-1720005938.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Meru%20International%20School%20has%20launched%20a%20daycare%20centre%20called%20Meru%20Aveksha%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fmeru-daycare-1720005938.jpeg%201512w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fmeru-daycare-1720005938-300x200.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fmeru-daycare-1720005938-500x333.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fmeru-daycare-1720005938-768x511.jpeg%20768w%